## 2. Call 도메인 (`maum` catalog)

음성 통화 세션 이력 관리. 실시간 상태는 **Redis**, 통화 이력은 **MySQL**, 통화 메타데이터(감정 분석 등)는 **DynamoDB** 저장을 권장합니다.

### MySQL Entity

```kotlin
// domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/call/CallRoomEntity.kt
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "call_room")
class CallRoomEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    val callerId: String,              // 발신자 userId
    val receiverId: String,            // 수신자 userId
    var status: Int = 1,               // 1: 요청중, 2: 통화중, 3: 종료, 4: 거절, 5: 미응답
    var startedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,
    var endedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,
    var durationSeconds: Int? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

### GraphQL Schema

```graphql
# graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/call.graphqls
type CallRoom {
    id: ID!
    caller: SimpleUser!
    receiver: SimpleUser!
    status: Int!
    startedAt: String
    endedAt: String
    durationSeconds: Int
    createdAt: String!
}

type CallHistory {
    items: [CallRoom!]!
    totalCount: Int!
}

extend type Query {
    myCallHistory(limit: Int, offset: Int): CallHistory!
    callRoom(callRoomId: ID!): CallRoom
}

extend type Mutation {
    requestCall(receiverId: ID!): CallRoom!
    acceptCall(callRoomId: ID!): CallRoom!
    rejectCall(callRoomId: ID!): CallRoom!
    endCall(callRoomId: ID!): CallRoom!
}
```

### gRPC Proto

```protobuf
// protobuf/src/main/proto/call/call.proto
syntax = "proto3";
package call;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.call";

service CallService {
  rpc RequestCall(RequestCallRequest) returns (RequestCallResponse);
  rpc AcceptCall(AcceptCallRequest)   returns (AcceptCallResponse);
  rpc RejectCall(RejectCallRequest)   returns (RejectCallResponse);
  rpc EndCall(EndCallRequest)         returns (EndCallResponse);
  rpc GetCallHistory(GetCallHistoryRequest) returns (GetCallHistoryResponse);
}

message CallRoomProto {
  string id          = 1;
  string caller_id   = 2;
  string receiver_id = 3;
  int32  status      = 4;
  optional string started_at        = 5;
  optional string ended_at          = 6;
